{"tid":1732523,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"［急］搵返壞電話既資料投訴狗","createTime":"2019-11-18T02:05:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T08:29:02.000Z","uid":72687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a940495a2085e8458e6c8b56a3c06583f65af261","tid":1732523,"uid":72687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:05:31.000Z","msg":"尋晚係尖東接放學俾狗查身分證，其中一個手足俾狗用電筒係咁照眼，我囉部電話影佢，佢就好大力推開我，部電話就跌壞左。<br />\n<br />\n有冇人知道個mon個感應跌壞左（mon冇碎），點樣用iTunes Back Up返d資料。<br />\n<br />\n插入iTunes，要求unlock左電話先可以Back Up。之後囉去整。打去apple佢地話資料會冇曬。<br />\n<br />\n我要搵返條片，投訴佢老母！<br />\n<br />\n人在尖東，有冇信得過既整電話鋪頭介紹。"},{"pid":"2c76055363d179f23a85b00fec44346d9d343425","tid":1732523,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:06:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1NdgS8Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1NdgS8Y.jpg&h=fb14efa1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n老豆搵仔呼籲<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你仲返工？去理大啦！</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不落單<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不譴責<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不退縮"},{"pid":"5ab1c83f761b4c7439986bb97e41a9fb6d89d718","tid":1732523,"uid":72687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:25:07.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"4f79ce96f5cf705b118d20d007a675911ee7a5fe","tid":1732523,"uid":128489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:38:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e2ad1d78ce20333a8a8a11eb5d652104674b07e9","tid":1732523,"uid":27441,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:40:26.000Z","msg":"其實.....告唔到"},{"pid":"378d6933360e1b25136c5768bc35104a7afc4379","tid":1732523,"uid":72687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:52:37.000Z","msg":"上網搵到用Lightni